2. The term “permanent establishment” includes especially: 

(a) a place of management; 

(b) a branch; 

(c) an office; 

(d) a factory; 

(e) a workshop, and 

(f) a mine, an oil or gas well, a quarry or any other place of exploration 

or extraction of natural resources.
